A great laptop can make a big difference to your working life and improve your efficiency by offering good performance and portability. Flagship professional laptops are ideal at fulfilling this role, and balance lightweight design and battery life with impressive performance. Some also include a number of modern features which can be a great help in a professional environment, from touchscreen displays to super-fast SSDs and discrete GPUs. To help you narrow down your next choice, we have listed the best professional laptops available to purchase in South Africa, according to expert reviews from around the web. Devices which are not available or not confirmed to launch in South Africa were excluded from the comparison.       